rovide a platform for a number of accompanying , technical workshops. thus , smaller and emerging communities can meet and develop more focussed topics or as yet less established topics. the unique organizational structure of a euro-par conference , which puts the hosting team in charge of both the scientific programme and the local organization , makes it a particularly lively and stimulating experience . the next euro-par conference will be euro-par 2014 in porto , portugal . ( c ) opyright by university of passau /.left-corner , /.right-corner , / # squeeze , / # center /container /layout
